        <p>A single-jurisdiction lawyer can only analyze your case from one legal system's perspective. A dual-licensed lawyer can evaluate both legal systems simultaneously, help you choose the more advantageous jurisdiction, and handle cross-border legal matters directly — without referring you to a separate specialist. Call 647-930-6688.</p>
